features: Light bulb is included: comes with a light bulb, 10000 hours life spend and 360° beam angle, soft lighting without flickering and noise and saves 90% of energy cost. The metal standing lamp is built-in an e26 screw base, you can make your stylish lamps with different shapes of any e26 base light bulb as you like. The floor lamp shade is compatible with a variety of led or incandescent light bulb(60w max).

Metal standing lamp: 65 inches x 10 inches, weight: 12.1 pounds. The lamp has a weighted base that prevents tipping, and the convenient to use pedal switch allows you to easily tap the lamp on or off with your foot.

Heavy metal base: the metal lamp is integrated with high-quality metal. Strong metal stem and weighted 9.8 inches metal base will firmly hold the standing light, provides stability and durability for daily use, 8 degree tilt test makes it wobble free and safe to have around children and pets.

Easy to assemble and move: the industrial floor lamp is easy assemble without tools, all you need to do is to screw all the parts of lamp pole together following the instruction. Come with detailed instructions and all hardware for quick and easy installation. 6 feet cord allows you to place the decorative tall pole lamp in any place you want.

Wide applications: it is a perfect floor lamps for bedrooms as well as a living room lamps, reading lamp, office lamp, baby’s nursery lamp, night light, bed lamp, decorative light source, etc.. It’s suitable for any decoration style such as retro, minimalist, industrial, rustic, modern, etc. it is also an ideal gift for your family and friend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Not a bad choice if you basically solely focused on price
reviews.reviewText: The QiMH Modern Floor Lamp for Living Room is an excellent addition to any home looking for a stylish and functional lighting solution. This lamp features a contemporary mid-century design that is both elegant and functional, with a tall pole and two sphere frosted glass globes.One of the standout features of the QiMH floor lamp is its gold finish, which adds a touch of elegance and sophistication to any room. The antique brass LED bulbs included with the lamp provide a warm, inviting glow that is perfect for creating a cozy atmosphere in any living space.The two sphere frosted glass globes are another highlight of this lamp. These globes provide a soft, diffused light that is perfect for reading, relaxing, or entertaining. They are also easy to clean and maintain, ensuring that your lamp will stay looking great for years to come.In terms of functionality, the QiMH floor lamp is easy to use and adjust. The tall pole allows you to position the globes at different heights, while the included LED bulbs provide long-lasting, energy-efficient lighting that is perfect for everyday use.Overall, the QiMH Modern Floor Lamp for Living Room is an excellent choice for anyone looking for a stylish and functional lighting solution. With its elegant design, warm lighting, and easy-to-use features, this lamp is sure to become a favorite in any home. Whether you're looking to create a cozy reading nook in your bedroom or add a touch of sophistication to your living room, the QiMH floor lamp is a great choice.
